description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

  

 

Do you tend to scrap your weight loss plan on the weekends? Corinne helps you bust through your excuses and shows you how to visualize not only how your weekend will play out but how you can feel great about your weekend come Monday morning. You'll also get a bonus tip from one of Corinne's tribe members on how to succeed on the weekend.
